snippet.title: The War of Genesis: Battle of Antaria - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Prepare your Airship by downloading NOW! 
Google Play Store: http://bit.ly/2IFXLRD

Go on an adventure in your own airship with memorable characters and giant Machina!
Combat fearsome monsters and the armies of Dark Armor to reclaim the continent of Antaria!
Experience captivating stories and become a true hero!

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/thewarofgenesis
Customer Support: https://gnss.zendesk.com/hc/en-us
